Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.96,tari-----STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\an8}日听：月長石  翻译：花解语 中校：散仙\N 日校：冷漠的风  时间轴：我见青山 压制：エロ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:38.48,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,感觉到胸中澎湃的声音时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:43.75,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,起跑线就出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.35,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,虽是一条看不见的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.91,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,也要开始奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.02,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,这样总比放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.25,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,更加让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.23,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,不安总在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:06.10,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,阻挡着自由的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.48,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,超越现在 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.14,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,把光明撒向那未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.72,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,在最初的轮回中 找到通往明天的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:23.71,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,前进中的我们怀有无尽的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:29.52,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,要相信闪耀的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:35.16,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,将永不放弃的力量用最大的爱包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.88,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,开始我们的旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:43.98,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,走向那崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}居然在这种时候眼前漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:52.23,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}难道说到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:53.96,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,绝对不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.74,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我们还有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:01.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我们还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:06.54,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 现在正是解放这个力量的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:16.36,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}凝聚大家希望的这柄剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:18.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.84,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}无上荣光的holy blade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:22.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:26.96,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}将勇气 将泪水 全都化作力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没有 一直在脑海中模拟这个情形 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:33.83,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}现在 去迎战强大的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真好啊  我也想站在这么大的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:34.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 弓道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:41.52,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Forever Forever Forever Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.58,0:02:36.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不是 我是说马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,马？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我想成为骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和全力奔跑的马一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:47.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,比任何人都先冲过终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶 很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:52.60,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂  别太闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,而且还没到恭喜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这才比赛第一回合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:04.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我们是要你抱着必胜的气势去拼搏啊 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.38,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你想让维恩白忙活一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:09.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那么那些异想天开的构思算怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:16.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:19.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你也一起来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,给 和奏的沙球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:33.03,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}现在 去迎战强大的敌人吧 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对不起 我今天身体不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.12,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是闹过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,来夏很喜欢庆典嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:00.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,庆典？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:05.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,呐 田中开始打羽球的契机是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,别用简称
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:11.99,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}白浜坂高校 田中大智选手 请到指定的比赛场地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:14.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,加油啊 奋起一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:16.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？ 那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,大智 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这是江户时代民众起义时所用的口号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:19.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}带着必死的觉悟把一整杯满载荣耀的酒水给…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:30.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:33.74,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:36.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,来了 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:39.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这个 有粉色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:46.56,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,粉色 啊 只有这里的这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:48.56,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,红色的也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,哎 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:54.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 欢迎回来 今天真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:55.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那么 就要这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不好意思 能给我倒杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,今天我来做晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那么 请到这边来付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,胜方 和田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.17,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,前八名的话 已经够厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:45.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:50.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不过如果是前四名的话就可以在全国大赛上出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,田中 好慢呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.70,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那顺便买瓶绿茶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:03.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,请您走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:05.53,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,帮我拿一下包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,谁哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.35,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,只是在脑中做模拟训练而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:25.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,趁现在记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,已经 不想再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.87,0:06:30.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,晴香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,田中是从什么时候开始打网球的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 大概是小学三年级开始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.26,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我开始社团活动后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:45.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,大智没多久就说「我也要去」 还想要自己的球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.36,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,小学就开始打了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:52.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,为什么不去羽毛球更加盛行的高中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没什么 白高的话 可以骑自行车上学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,以前部员也更多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我有个仰慕的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:04.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,也是我们高中出身的… 之类的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 是因为有那位选手才开始打羽球的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.85,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,叫你别用简称了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:15.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:16.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:22.22,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,为了夏天也能避免着凉所以有热的卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,搞什么呀这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.67,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 纱羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:34.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,最近有点无精打采的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.40,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈 水好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:51.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,咦 纱羽的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:59.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是志保哦 疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.38,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,久违地闯祸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对纱羽要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.39,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那家伙 动不动就要说「你已经不年轻了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真是一年比一年神气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你们 感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 在那边随便放下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,出了很多汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,要不要泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶 啊 不用了 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:38.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对了 你稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:46.69,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是这个吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:50.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我也是白校毕业的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,算是和奏酱的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:56.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,以前这一带呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:02.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不是上白高就是上镰高的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,看 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是和奏的妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真昼学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.28,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:14.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对吧 她比我大一级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这位是高仓学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.35,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,高仓直子 现在是教导主任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.09,0:09:26.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我给你复印一份完整的 下回来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:31.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那时候大家 都是合唱团的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:35.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是哦 在大赛取得优胜后拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没听你妈妈说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,病情都没跟她说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:50.13,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是啊 那孩子不是备考嘛 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 等一下 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那个我来弄就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:02.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:11.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天的晚饭要我来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:14.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶 啊 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你今天很闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.17,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 没有 很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.16,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真是的 小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:25.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,听说妈妈昏倒真是吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那是大家夸大其词了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这回也很快就能出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我去换条抹布回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈 要好好爱惜身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:49.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和和奏一起写歌的话 说不定就可以好起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.84,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,来 让我听听和奏的点子和意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我不是说没时间干那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,马上就要参加考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:02.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那一起唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没那个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:11.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,火气太大会影响实力发挥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你以为是谁的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:19.62,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,惹你生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:21.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:27.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,一起写歌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,就能好起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.88,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 你能不能好好教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.11,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这根本不是什么练习曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.11,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你小时候就经常这样和我一起唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:53.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,虽然学习也很重要 但考试会结束 音乐却会持续哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:57.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,为了音乐能一直伴随和奏左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.82,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,千万不要忘记 爱着音乐的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:00.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,学校都考不上的话说这些还有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,闪着腰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶 那么星期六你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:28.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我就星期一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没什么 这种事就要大家互相关照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:36.22,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,好 那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,远野的叔叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:41.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 又是腰出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:45.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,下周一我打算去田里帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.17,0:12:45.60,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:50.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,秀彦是上班族似乎请不了急假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,但是大概要去两三天 你没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真是 我也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,晚饭 要不要叫寿司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:09.88,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,房间里的钢琴 我想处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:22.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,如果交给真正喜欢音乐的人使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,想必妈妈也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,CD只要有个小收录机就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,其它用不着的东西也处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.40,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,腾出来的地方放张床什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:37.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那我明天打电话问问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:41.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:55.19,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,关东地区今晨云层开始扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:59.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,目前强烈低气压正自小笠原群岛近海北上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:04.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,受其影响午后至傍晚的天气将可能十分恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:16.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 会补习到很晚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,还是带上雨衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,风好像也越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:21.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,今天会有人来拿钢琴和其它那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:32.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯 我会整理清楚的 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:33.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.69,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,金鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是金鱼啦 金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.76,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是鲸鱼啦 鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那 折中一下当它是海豚先生好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:10.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,海豚先生在唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,哦 我也三点半就走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,有什么事就给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:42.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,叔叔那里手机信号不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不过远野的电话你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:46.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,晚饭可以叫寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,说了我不会有事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:49.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,你走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:52.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.99,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,今天待会儿有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,可以的话一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,为了庆祝大智进入前八强 要开派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:45.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天想在下雨之前买好东西回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:17:00.13,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,现在开始羽毛球大赛的庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:01.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,田中请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,诶 可是蛋糕也买了和奏那份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,有很大草莓的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,就来吃一下蛋糕也行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.26,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,抱歉 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.82,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,果然 没什么精神呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不会是讨厌草莓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.81,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没那可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,难道是 我太烦人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这倒是有点可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:44.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:32.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:58.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,喂 妈妈 不是叫你帮我把雨衣拿出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 现在就帮你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真是的 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:07.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,自己的东西自己准备好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,准考证带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:10.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没有忘了东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那就走好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.19,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这个 可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,这种东西又无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,会淋湿的 赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:11.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,今后的路想和女儿… 和和奏一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,不管健康的时候还是生病的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.39,0:20:21.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,高兴的时候还是悲伤的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:27.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,那样的歌 感觉和和奏一起就能写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:34.18,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,因为对我来说 歌曲是传达爱的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:41.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,是和奏教会了我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:46.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,想要对她传达的感情便化成了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:49.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,如果能够一起唱出这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:55.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,如果能够听到来自和奏的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:02.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我的人生 就太圆满了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,还没说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:22.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,「我出门了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:25.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,还有「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:36.54,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,再也不能一起唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:14.16,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,无论是晴天还是雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:20.98,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,只要有你们在身边 我总能露出笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:26.88,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,直到记忆的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.31,0:22:34.54,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,倾听记忆中摇晃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:40.88,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,来  把手递给我 与我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:48.80,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,在不是一个人的空间里 尽情欢乐的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:54.53,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,愉快的风吹拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.57,0:23:01.84,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,有时欢笑有时哭泣有时放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:07.65,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,接着敞开自己的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:19.80,tari--OP-CN,,0,0,0,,轻哼记忆里的旋律 奏响乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:32.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.98,0:23:36.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,和奏 你觉得我们首先最需要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:36.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:38.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂 和奏 接下来有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:39.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:06.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,我带了一个可靠的伙伴 来代替我守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:07.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0,0,0,,红钢铁战士 登场
